Muchidzidzo cheScience, [[dendera]] (rotation, revolution) izwi rinoshandiswa kutsanangudza kana chiumbwa chichipoterera akiso yekufungidzira (imaginary axis) zvikuru sei kana akiso iri kunze kwechiumbwa ichochi. 

Muenzaniso kufamba kunoita nyika mu[[Boterekwa]] mainotenderera ichipoterera zuva. Dendera rinoguma kuverengwa paratangira kuverengwa. Sokuti nyika inoita dendera pazuva kamwe (1) pagore.
